node.title: Police at Manukau velodrome after death of man with critical injuries
node.description: Police are at the Manukau velodrome as they investigate the death of a man who arrived at Auckland's Middlemore Hospital with critical injuries.
node.content:
["Police are investigating the death of a man who arrived at Auckland's Middlemore Hospital with critical injuries.", "", "
The man arrived at Middlemore Hospital with critical injuries but later died. Photo: LDR / Stephen Forbes
", "He died shortly after he arrived at around 6am this morning.", "Police have set up a scene examination at the Manukau velodrome in an effort to work out what happened."]
